OL,3,C'Bionic peer' thanks wife who rejected
OL,4,Cdo not resuscitate order
OL,6,F"I have to give thanks to my dear
OL,7,Fwife, now Lady Mackinlay, for her
OL,8,Fforthrightness, her robustness, her
OL,9,Finsistence that a DNR notice and
OL,10,Fpalliative care was not in order for
OL,11,Fme, and that they should fight for me
OL,12,Ftill the end."
OL,14,FThe former MP for South Thanet
OL,15,Fdeveloped sepsis from pneumonia,
OL,16,Fdespite having no symptoms of the
OL,17,Frespiratory infection. About 48,000
OL,18,Fpeople die from sepsis each year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]
