OL,3,C'Bionic peer' thanks wife who rejected
OL,4,Cdo not resuscitate order
OL,6,FHe met Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Flast week to discuss a change to
OL,8,Ftreatment focused on the "patient, not
OL,9,Fa menu and a page of what we usually
OL,10,Fdo".
OL,12,F"There will be many, many thousands
OL,13,Ffor which lives can be saved or bits
OL,14,Fand pieces can be saved," he said on
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUrD@CO]tD@AOUvD@YO]
