OL,3,C'Bionic peer' thanks wife who rejected
OL,4,Cdo not resuscitate order
OL,6,F"This is easily solvable if you find
OL,7,Fit early, if you recognise it early,
OL,8,Fif you can recognise that your loved
OL,9,Fone is feeling possibly the worst that
OL,10,Fthey have ever felt in the whole of
OL,11,Ftheir life. And thankfully my wife
OL,12,Fasked that question, 'Could this be
OL,13,Fsepsis'?"
OL,15,FHe continued: "I was unlucky. Many
OL,16,Fpeople go through sepsis and they may
OL,17,Flose nothing. They might find
OL,18,Fthemselves with brain fog, they might
OL,19,Ffind themselves with temporary
OL,20,Fconditions that may recover.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]wD@OOU
