OL,3,C'Bionic peer' thanks wife who rejected
OL,4,Cdo not resuscitate order
OL,6,F"Now the prosthetics you see here are
OL,7,Ftrial ones. I know we shouldn't be
OL,8,Fusing props in this place, but I hope
OL,9,Fnoble lords may forgive me today.
OL,10,FThese are provided by the private
OL,11,Fsector, these are on trial.
OL,13,F"Because the NHS, obviously not
OL,14,Fwishing to spend too much money on
OL,15,Fperhaps items that aren't going to get
OL,16,Fused, might give me these in year
OL,17,Fthree. But I want to get on with life
OL,18,Fin year one and I'm doing that with
OL,19,Fthese types of prosthetics."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@\O]
