OL,3,C'Bionic peer' thanks wife who rejected
OL,4,Cdo not resuscitate order
OL,6,FFollowing Lord Mackinlay, Conservative
OL,7,Fpeer Lord Lilley said: "Lord Mackinley
OL,8,Fis a friend of mine who I had known
OL,9,Fbefore his illness to be as courageous
OL,10,Fintellectually as he proved to be
OL,11,Fphysically.
OL,13,F"He is a fighter and a winner, and
OL,14,Fmercifully his wife Kati is also a
OL,15,Ffighter. And we are grateful to her
OL,16,Ffor ensuring that Lord Mackinley is
OL,17,Fwith us today."
